{"tid":988233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做deadlift（硬拉） 既時候點樣可以細聲啲","createTime":"2019-01-20T01:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T22:53:55.000Z","uid":161664,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b94989124e9cea73215c2a6f861711334780507d","tid":988233,"uid":161664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁既，之前城大體育館個天花咪 塌左既，佢個gym room 就搬左去圖書館上面既open area, 結果我一做deadlift, 個管理員叔叔就叫我細聲啲，話樓下圖書館投訴， 咁我都明白佢難處嘅，咁我就係 槓鈴下面加咗兩塊餅，等成件事細聲啲。。<br />\n但琴日我一如以往地做deadlift ，第2個叔叔又走過黎叫我細聲啲，我已經諗唔到其他方法， 冇理由做錯嘅姿勢等成件事細聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後個叔叔話 其實你都唔夠力拉上胸口㗎喇，做輕啲啦， 正確的姿勢應該係一啲聲都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗佢真係唔識架喎🤔<br />\n<br />\nDeadlift新手 110kg x6x4<br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"db663a567c89f1b7ceb25b4fe78ecdc4d9b9df86","tid":988233,"uid":9387,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢咩<br />\n叫佢試下點無聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6f1ff2ae9d6951d408580c18d85623b8498ec2","tid":988233,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母囉 讀到大學仲要人教？"},{"pid":"e322dfe28e2dd5028534170e65e61e7d2f74eff5","tid":988233,"uid":109655,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"原來就係你 成日砰砰聲 你做一次我投訴一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fc4e112d3050d4e8803b02363a56e490cadd98","tid":988233,"uid":131078,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"佢真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫佢做幾set 黎睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0da638976a29318d1678b39bca8a9744e02c